  "sequence_id": "step5",
  "source": {
    "plain_text": "Sharpe Ratio: SR_p = (E(R_p) - R_f)/sigma_p. Sortino Ratio: similar but focuses on downside risk. Treynor Ratio: (E(R_p) - R_f)/beta_p. Jensen's Alpha: alpha_p = E(R_p) - [R_f + beta_p (E(R_M) - R_f)].",
    "related": [
      "Performance Measures"
    ]
  },
